{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01UWhHUYE4jAUxbhybQYEt4W","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Excellent! All the changes have been successfully applied. Let me create a summary of what was refactored:\n\n## Refactoring Summary\n\nI have successfully refactored all Java files in the application package from Jakarta EE 8 to Quarkus. Here's a detailed breakdown of the changes made:\n\n### 1. Interface Files (Updated javax.* to jakarta.*)\n\n**BookingService.java** (`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/application/BookingService.java`)\n- Changed `javax.validation.*` to `jakarta.validation.*`\n\n**CargoInspectionService.java** (`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/application/CargoInspectionService.java`)\n- Changed `javax.validation.*` to `jakarta.validation.*`\n\n**HandlingEventService.java** (`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/application/HandlingEventService.java`)\n- Changed `javax.validation.*` to `jakarta.validation.*`\n\n**ApplicationEvents.java** - No changes needed (no javax imports)\n\n### 2. Implementation Classes (Replaced EJB with CDI + Transactional)\n\n**internal/DefaultBookingService.java** (`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/application/internal/DefaultBookingService.java`)\n- Replaced `javax.ejb.Stateless` with `jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped` + `jakarta.transaction.Transactional`\n- Replaced `javax.inject.Inject` with `jakarta.inject.Inject`\n- Changed `@Stateless` annotation to `@ApplicationScoped` and `@Transactional` on class level\n\n**internal/DefaultCargoInspectionService.java** (`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/application/internal/DefaultCargoInspectionService.java`)\n- Replaced `javax.ejb.Stateless` with `jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped` + `jakarta.transaction.Transactional`\n- Replaced `javax.inject.Inject` with `jakarta.inject.Inject`\n- Changed `@Stateless` annotation to `@ApplicationScoped` and `@Transactional` on class level\n\n**internal/DefaultHandlingEventService.java** (`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/application/internal/DefaultHandlingEventService.java`)\n- Replaced `javax.ejb.Stateless` with `jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped` + `jakarta.transaction.Transactional`\n- Replaced `javax.inject.Inject` with `jakarta.inject.Inject`\n- Changed `@Stateless` annotation to `@ApplicationScoped` and `@Transactional` on class level\n\n### 3. Utility Classes\n\n**util/RestConfiguration.java** (`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/application/util/RestConfiguration.java`)\n- Completely rewritten to remove Jersey-specific ServerProperties reference\n- Changed `javax.ws.rs.*` to `jakarta.ws.rs.*`\n- Simplified to basic JAX-RS Application class\n\n**util/ApplicationSettings.java** (`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/application/util/ApplicationSettings.java`)\n- Replaced `javax.persistence.*` with `jakarta.persistence.*`\n\n**util/SampleDataGenerator.java** (`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/application/util/SampleDataGenerator.java`)\n- Replaced `javax.ejb.Singleton` with `jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped`\n- Removed `javax.ejb.Startup` (replaced with Quarkus StartupEvent pattern)\n- Replaced `javax.ejb.TransactionAttribute*` with `jakarta.transaction.Transactional`\n- Removed `javax.annotation.PostConstruct` (replaced with `@Observes StartupEvent`)\n- Replaced `javax.inject.Inject` with `jakarta.inject.Inject`\n- Replaced `javax.persistence.*` with `jakarta.persistence.*`\n- Added Quarkus imports: `io.quarkus.runtime.StartupEvent` and `jakarta.enterprise.event.Observes`\n- Changed method signature from `@PostConstruct public void loadSampleData()` to `@Transactional void onStart(@Observes StartupEvent event)`\n\n**util/DateConverter.java** - No changes needed (no javax imports)\n\nAll business logic has been preserved. The refactoring only changed the framework-specific imports and annotations from Jakarta EE 8 to Quarkus-compatible equivalents."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a4072757-006a-493f-88e0-08a9064c7917","uuid":"3eeced71-b965-45bb-999b-12a731af319b"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929","id":"msg_bdrk_01DaYkMndMQyHNA2x6ybr48r","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_011Dup4Au91r4xVx3rHCtvoe","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/jms/JmsApplicationEvents.java","content":"package org.eclipse.cargotracker.infrastructure.messaging.jms;\n\nimport java.io.Serializable;\nimport java.util.logging.Level;\nimport java.util.logging.Logger;\nimport jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped;\nimport jakarta.enterprise.event.Event;\nimport jakarta.inject.Inject;\nimport org.eclipse.cargotracker.application.ApplicationEvents;\nimport org.eclipse.cargotracker.domain.model.cargo.Cargo;\nimport org.eclipse.cargotracker.domain.model.handling.HandlingEvent;\nimport org.eclipse.cargotracker.interfaces.handling.HandlingEventRegistrationAttempt;\n\n@ApplicationScoped\npublic class JmsApplicationEvents implements ApplicationEvents, Serializable {\n\n  private static final long serialVersionUID = 1L;\n\n  @Inject private Logger logger;\n\n  @Inject private Event<CargoHandledEvent> cargoHandledEvent;\n  @Inject private Event<MisdirectedCargoEvent> misdirectedCargoEvent;\n  @Inject private Event<DeliveredCargoEvent> deliveredCargoEvent;\n  @Inject private Event<HandlingEventRegistrationAttempt> handlingEventRegistrationEvent;\n\n  @Override\n  public void cargoWasHandled(HandlingEvent event) {\n    Cargo cargo = event.getCargo();\n    logger.log(Level.INFO, \"Cargo was handled {0}\", cargo);\n    cargoHandledEvent.fire(new CargoHandledEvent(cargo.getTrackingId().getIdString()));\n  }\n\n  @Override\n  public void cargoWasMisdirected(Cargo cargo) {\n    logger.log(Level.INFO, \"Cargo was misdirected {0}\", cargo);\n    misdirectedCargoEvent.fire(new MisdirectedCargoEvent(cargo.getTrackingId().getIdString()));\n  }\n\n  @Override\n  public void cargoHasArrived(Cargo cargo) {\n    logger.log(Level.INFO, \"Cargo has arrived {0}\", cargo);\n    deliveredCargoEvent.fire(new DeliveredCargoEvent(cargo.getTrackingId().getIdString()));\n  }\n\n  @Override\n  public void receivedHandlingEventRegistrationAttempt(HandlingEventRegistrationAttempt attempt) {\n    logger.log(Level.INFO, \"Received handling event registration attempt {0}\", attempt);\n    handlingEventRegistrationEvent.fire(attempt);\n  }\n\n  // CDI Event classes\n  public static class CargoHandledEvent {\n    private final String trackingId;\n    public CargoHandledEvent(String trackingId) { this.trackingId = trackingId; }\n    public String getTrackingId() { return trackingId; }\n  }\n\n  public static class MisdirectedCargoEvent {\n    private final String trackingId;\n    public MisdirectedCargoEvent(String trackingId) { this.trackingId = trackingId; }\n    public String getTrackingId() { return trackingId; }\n  }\n\n  public static class DeliveredCargoEvent {\n    private final String trackingId;\n    public DeliveredCargoEvent(String trackingId) { this.trackingId = trackingId; }\n    public String getTrackingId() { return trackingId; }\n  }\n}\n"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":5,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2048,"cache_read_input_tokens":28100,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":2048,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":2735},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01WFKJNr1QAUBPqrBix5WkQG","session_id":"a4072757-006a-493f-88e0-08a9064c7917","uuid":"2b28a565-b704-4bc3-b978-dfc577c80b68"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929","id":"msg_bdrk_01DaYkMndMQyHNA2x6ybr48r","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01J2hWYBjc57qgVyBVz5ga9r","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/jms/CargoHandledConsumer.java","content":"package org.eclipse.cargotracker.infrastructure.messaging.jms;\n\nimport java.util.logging.Level;\nimport java.util.logging.Logger;\nimport jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped;\nimport jakarta.enterprise.event.Observes;\nimport jakarta.inject.Inject;\nimport org.eclipse.cargotracker.application.CargoInspectionService;\nimport org.eclipse.cargotracker.domain.model.cargo.TrackingId;\n\n@ApplicationScoped\npublic class CargoHandledConsumer {\n\n  @Inject private Logger logger;\n  @Inject private CargoInspectionService cargoInspectionService;\n\n  public void onCargoHandled(@Observes JmsApplicationEvents.CargoHandledEvent event) {\n    logger.log(Level.INFO, \"Cargo handled event received for {0}\", event.getTrackingId());\n    cargoInspectionService.inspectCargo(new TrackingId(event.getTrackingId()));\n  }\n}\n"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":5,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2048,"cache_read_input_tokens":28100,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":2048,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":2735},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01WFKJNr1QAUBPqrBix5WkQG","session_id":"a4072757-006a-493f-88e0-08a9064c7917","uuid":"446d71d1-321f-490e-b087-d0351e658897"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929","id":"msg_bdrk_01DaYkMndMQyHNA2x6ybr48r","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01AQbmedoyQM7g2sV6Y5evCh","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/jms/HandlingEventRegistrationAttemptConsumer.java","content":"package org.eclipse.cargotracker.infrastructure.messaging.jms;\n\nimport java.util.logging.Level;\nimport java.util.logging.Logger;\nimport jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped;\nimport jakarta.enterprise.event.Observes;\nimport jakarta.inject.Inject;\nimport org.eclipse.cargotracker.application.HandlingEventService;\nimport org.eclipse.cargotracker.domain.model.handling.CannotCreateHandlingEventException;\nimport org.eclipse.cargotracker.interfaces.handling.HandlingEventRegistrationAttempt;\n\n@ApplicationScoped\npublic class HandlingEventRegistrationAttemptConsumer {\n\n  @Inject private HandlingEventService handlingEventService;\n  @Inject private Logger logger;\n\n  public void onHandlingEventRegistration(@Observes HandlingEventRegistrationAttempt attempt) {\n    try {\n      handlingEventService.registerHandlingEvent(\n          attempt.getCompletionTime(),\n          attempt.getTrackingId(),\n          attempt.getVoyageNumber(),\n          attempt.getUnLocode(),\n          attempt.getType());\n    } catch (CannotCreateHandlingEventException e) {\n      logger.log(Level.SEVERE, \"Error processing handling event registration\", e);\n    }\n  }\n}\n"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":5,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2048,"cache_read_input_tokens":28100,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":2048,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":2735},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_0