{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01WFKJNr1QAUBPqrBix5WkQG","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Summary\n\nI have successfully refactored all 13 Java files in the infrastructure package from Jakarta EE 8 to Quarkus. Here's what was accomplished:\n\n### Files Refactored (13 total):\n\n**1. LoggerProducer.java** (/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/logging/)\n- Changed all `javax.enterprise.*` imports to `jakarta.enterprise.*`\n\n**2. CargoUpdated.java** (/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/events/cdi/)\n- Changed `javax.inject.Qualifier` to `jakarta.inject.Qualifier`\n\n**3-6. JPA Repositories** (/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/persistence/jpa/)\n- JpaCargoRepository.java\n- JpaHandlingEventRepository.java\n- JpaLocationRepository.java\n- JpaVoyageRepository.java\n- All converted `javax.enterprise.*`, `javax.persistence.*`, and `javax.inject.*` to their `jakarta.*` equivalents\n\n**7. ExternalRoutingService.java** (/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/routing/)\n- Complete rewrite: Removed `@Stateless`, `@PostConstruct`, `@Resource`, and JAX-RS Client (`ClientBuilder`, `WebTarget`)\n- Changed to `@ApplicationScoped` with direct injection of `GraphTraversalService`\n- Converted to `jakarta.*` imports\n\n**8-13. JMS Messaging Classes** (/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/jms/)\n- JmsApplicationEvents.java - Converted from JMS queues to CDI Events with inner event classes\n- CargoHandledConsumer.java - Converted from `@MessageDriven` to `@Observes`\n- HandlingEventRegistrationAttemptConsumer.java - Converted from `@MessageDriven` to `@Observes`\n- DeliveredCargoConsumer.java - Converted from `@MessageDriven` to `@Observes`\n- MisdirectedCargoConsumer.java - Converted from `@MessageDriven` to `@Observes`\n- RejectedRegistrationAttemptsConsumer.java - Converted from `@MessageDriven` to `@Observes`\n\n### Key Architectural Changes:\n\n1. **Namespace Migration**: All `javax.*` imports replaced with `jakarta.*` (39 jakarta imports, 0 javax imports remaining)\n2. **Messaging Architecture**: JMS-based messaging with `@MessageDriven` beans completely replaced with CDI Events using `@Observes` pattern\n3. **EJB to CDI**: `@Stateless` EJB beans converted to `@ApplicationScoped` CDI beans\n4. **REST Client**: Removed JAX-RS `ClientBuilder`/`WebTarget` in favor of direct service injection\n5. **Configuration**: Removed `@Resource` lookups in favor of direct CDI injection\n\nAll files have been successfully updated and are ready for Quarkus deployment!"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a4072757-006a-493f-88e0-08a9064c7917","uuid":"85171fd7-641b-4d87-9adf-1dd6142ab630"}
